            <Label lineSpacing="2.0" minWidth="-Infinity" prefWidth="1200.0" text="Select the service request page for the request you are looking to create from either the side menu or the systems service page. You must fill out all the fields on the request page before submitting otherwise the request will not submit. For each page this will include at least &#10;- Location of where the request needs to be done&#10;- Assignment to the staff memeber that is expected to complete the request&#10;- Status whether the request has been completed or not ( you will most likely set this to waiting  when you create the request)&#10;Then you hit the submit button and you will get a ouhs notification to show it has gone through, or you can hit cancel and it will reset the page&#10;" textFill="#477ccc" wrapText="true" GridPane.halignment="LEFT" GridPane.hgrow="ALWAYS" GridPane.valignment="CENTER">
